A new version of Translation is out. on* properties of FileLoader were marked as deprecated, it was the intent in previous version, they just did not get the appropriate phpDoc. Option onUntranslated of Nette DIC extension throws a deprecation warning with non-default values.

MessageSelector is deprecated in favor of new IntervalsMessageSelector. Interface IMessageSelector will renamed to MessageSelector in the next major version.

For complete list of changes since previous version, see CHANGELOG.md.
